edu.cs495.engine.game

Class AbstractLevel

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.cs495.engine.game.AbstractLevel
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Estate, SurfaceWorld

    public abstract class AbstractLevel
extends java.lang.Object
    An abstract game level object models a level of a game. This holds several attributes such as the background of the level, objects in the level, and more used for updating and rendering.
    Version:
    February 2019
    Author:
    Spencer Imbleau
